milestones.description: Ranatunga has become the top scorer for SL in ODIs with 3632 runs, going past de Silva's 3579
Ranatunga and Ruwan Kalpage's 132-run partnership is SL's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 109 between de Silva and Ruwan Kalpage
Ranatunga has broken the record for most ODIs (62) as captain for SL, going past Duleep Mendis
